<body>

<div class="section">
    <h1>ü§ñüí• CHIEF KNOCK-A-HOMER: FUTURAMA GLADIATOR EDITION üèÜ<br>Japan Underground Tournament Destroyer + Fight Simulator</h1>
    <p>Homer meets Bender in the Ultimate Robot Fighting League. Swarm-powered beast with three personas. Now with interactive fight simulator ‚Äì watch our garage monster destroy the competition!</p>
</div>

<div class="section">
    <h2>Interactive Arena Simulator</h2>
    <p>Click START FIGHT to see Chief Knock-A-Homer (blue) vs Destructor-style opponent (red). Watch the swarm spin-up, persona switches, and pure destruction.</p>
    <canvas id="arena" width="800" height="500"></canvas>
    <div class="controls">
        <button onclick="startFight()">START FIGHT</button>
        <button onclick="resetFight()">RESET</button>
    </div>
    <div id="log"></div>
