        <li><strong>Gender Bender Troll Mode:</strong> Pink panels ‚Äì confuses opponent AI.</li>
        <li><strong>Final Destructor Mode:</strong> Full swarm + smoke effect + "I WILL DESTROY YOU!" roar.</li>
    </ul>
