<div class="section">
    <h2>Why It Wins Every Time</h2>
    <p>Swarm of 130 cheap Chinese drone motors ‚Üí instant 18,000 RPM. Redundancy means it survives hits that kill single-motor bots. Persona switches add chaos ‚Äì opponents never know what‚Äôs coming.</p>
